quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  25,33,Futhi abakwazi ukukulethela isibonelo ngaphandle kokuthi sikulethela iqiniso nencazelo engcono kunayo
  25,34,Labo abayoqoqelwa ndawonye esihogweni ngobuso babo labo basendaweni embi futhi baphambuke kakhulu endleleni
  25,35,Futhi ngempela samnikeza uMose incwadi futhi sabeka umfowabo u-Aroni kanye naye njengomsizi
  25,36,"Sabe sesithi, “nobabili hambani niye ebantwini labo ababephika amavesi ethu sabe sesibabhubhisa ngembubhiso ephelele”"
  25,37,Nabantu baNowa ngenkathi bephika izithunywa sabaminzisa futhi sabenza ukuthi babe nguphawu ebantwini futhi izoni sazilungiselela isijeziso esibuhlungu
  25,38,No-A’d noThamud nezihlali zaseRass nezizukulwane eziningi maphakathi
  25,39,Futhi kuleso naleso sizwe sanikeza isibonelo futhi ngamunye wabo sambhubhisa ngembubhiso ephelele
  25,40,"Futhi ngempela bahamba badlula edolobheni elalinethwe yimvula enzima, ngakube abaliboni yini na? Qha abakwethembi ukuvuswa (ngosuku lokuvuswa kwabafileyo)"
  25,41,Futhi uma bekubona abakuthathi njengento yalutho ngaphandle kokukwenza inhlekisa (bathi) “ngakube nguyena lona uMvelinqangi amthuma njengesithunywa yini na?”
  25,42,"Ucishe wasiphambukisa koNkulunkulu bethu, ukube asizange sibabekezelele, futhi bayokwazi ngenkathi besibona isijeziso ukuthi ngubani ophambuke ngokwedlulele endleleni"
  25,43,Ngakube umbonile yini lowo othatha izifiso zakhe njengoNkulunkulu bakhe na? Ngakube wena uzoba ngumlondi wakhe na